{"tid":473551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人骨子裡咪又係中國人","createTime":"2017-11-19T10:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T12:44:15.000Z","uid":19932,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4852ee837a39a390bb6bcbfe3ec2143f5a1bd38d","tid":473551,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T10:54:56.000Z","msg":"自私自利 共產過共產 。<br />\n<br />\n交通塞車Post 一大班人屌窮人揸車 阻交通 撞車叫人死全家。<br />\n都痴撚線 人地想撞車？唔關心受傷者都算 只關心自己幾時翻到去？ <br />\n窮人揾到小小錢 養得起㗎車 又屌佢地阻交通。而唔係諗下問題根本？ 交通規劃呢？考車制度？ 政府實施？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n響喉Post 更加厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一大堆 有錢揸跑車就可以嘈嘅概念 mk仔h車就錯哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  利申 我唔贊成仼何人改車<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再嚟今日丁權post 真係忍無可忍 人地原住民早幾百年落嚟捱 個陣咁撚艱苦 又英又日嘅洗禮 到現㗎好景小小 又葡萄人 人地都未撚怪啲舊移民蝗 。真係笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n自己人唔撐自己人 學人搞分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港配有民主？"},{"pid":"bd8e506ed80db9632f342620f39aecb264fa37b5","tid":473551,"uid":19932,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T10:59:55.000Z","msg":"歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d374b85606c5aa5ee742c049e10800ecbfe4f5","tid":473551,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:00:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4470c61cb3198af7d1fe275d57589a3ea74d870d","tid":473551,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:00:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d33f43c3f8cd53bf5b82d86727ee9374e1fb7971","tid":473551,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:02:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩人都緊要 最重要就係有處女女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見到成個感情台就真係厲害 。同時事台個對比大到<br />\n假如呢個平台大部份人支持香港獨立 就真係知咩叫失敗<br />\n八婆八公post就最注重。"},{"pid":"e5df1238799497a85347056a7bc0977cb90654ea","tid":473551,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:04:36.000Z","msg":"你搵連登黎代表全部香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9861964e833e579cdb25801831b41069a5d2369","tid":473551,"uid":140599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:07:07.000Z","msg":"岩呀樓主 家下連登就係少有你呢啲人"},{"pid":"5f583d3a987cd65503ab7dfebbdab07c20cec693","tid":473551,"uid":19932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你搵連登黎代表全部香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我繼續講<br />\n對人無禮 完全睇唔到受過高等教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比小小錢 以為自己高人一等 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我相信做服務行業就知道 。有錢個班閪撚到 反而紋身古惑仔咁款仲有禮貌會體諒下人<br />\n撘車現㗎排隊嘅禮儀 每況愈下。 收工時間去地鐵留意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704f5d5e310e45e8e124543ffaf1c70c534c6e7c","tid":473551,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:09:48.000Z","msg":"繼續負評啦 我開得post就預左<br />\n有咩不滿 大家討論下"},{"pid":"8eef45428b73d8c056fb15b3f1fbf8fd9a33c4e4","tid":473551,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:15:17.000Z","msg":"仲記得前幾個月 遊行post 連登吊到幾多個廿歲左右嘅青年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為左個小小錢 出賣香港 都夠膽死話自己黃絲 真係笑而不語。<br />\n雙十一 淘寶Post唔講咁多啦 大家有眼睇<br />\n口中講到幾討厭中共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  身體卻。。。"},{"pid":"ca3305b328703a25e4eb91bc7c51b7d14c75e5c8","tid":473551,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b3e8d267f15208a59f2f32dcf0c9477cae46a6","tid":473551,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"154bc74472f56d818de46bcda3817bc8e0bd53a0","tid":473551,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:31:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1ae27c7afcbf89f079e942320e7525c357244d0e","tid":473551,"uid":124036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"咁香港人係歷史咁計 香港係唔係都係屬於中國？ <br />\n利申：唔識所以問"}]}